{"tid":1742821,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我地再唔反醒，黎明行動真係會停","createTime":"2019-11-21T02:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T04:31:55.000Z","uid":63822,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"321e803fc654a2b1c98282dc8c7ad2f6b3bb2e50","tid":1742821,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"首先我強調，黎明行動係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔可以停</span><br />\n<br />\n但我地開始面對幾個困難，唔改一改玩法既話係會逼死自己<br />\n<br />\n幫大家整理一下個思路先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黎明行動</span><br />\n<br />\n目的：衝擊香港經濟，直接cut中共收入<br />\n<br />\n方法：透過罷工、罷課、罷市，務求令香港停止運作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上星期</span><br />\n<br />\n面對困難：香港人好中意返工，主動罷工難過登天<br />\n<br />\n對策：塞交通，逼你罷工<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n一個星期過去，我地睇睇而家乜野情況<br />\n<br />\n面對困難：<br />\n<br />\n1）香港人熱愛返工，遇強愈強，手足用盡方法都只能令港豬遲到，做唔到停工<br />\n<br />\n2）令部分淺藍變深藍、港豬變淺藍，增加不必要敵人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3）過份focus罷工，甚少人針對個市</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁講一講我有乜野提議啦，不過一個人腦力有限，希望大家集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n對策：<br />\n1）無謂硬碰，死轉牛角尖，快閃式塞交通。火警鐘又好，落車同時緊急掣又好<br />\n<br />\n塞到就塞，塞唔到就算啦<br />\n<br />\n原理同唔好打陣地戰一樣，你塞死一個車箱，不如站站拉一拉緊急掣就落車走人，效率更高<br />\n<br />\n路面野都係同一原則<br />\n<br />\n2）行動完就算，唔好同住何人發生口角<br />\n<br />\n再進一步係R下藍屍吹水<br />\n<br />\n「唉，又搞搞震，又遲到啦<br />\n<br />\n咁多後生仔捉十年都捉唔哂啦，拿拿聲應承咩咩五大壽頭咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n我日日五點出門口都遲到，政府再唔哄掂班人，我好快比人炒嫁啦」<br />\n<br />\n扮藍，散播失敗主義，再推返個波比政府<br />\n<br />\n3）唔好all in罷工，三罷係有分先後次序<br />\n<br />\n罷市為大，罷工為次，罷課為小<br />\n<br />\n國際金融中心呀，個市先係春袋<br />\n<br />\n日日裝佢老母港交所修，裝到佢停市<br />\n<br />\n停唔到就裝修到佢怕，怕到要好似理大咁重兵包圍<br />\n<br />\n裝唔到港交所就裝修紅色黑色上市公司，裝到佢股價插水，自已停牌收皮<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n我認為黎明行動係將假日抗爭變成365抗爭，晚間變日間既關鍵，唔停得<br />\n<br />\n但認同現階段模式係吃力不討好，有點似玩鳩全世界包括自己<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動（泛指一至五日間活動）絕不能停，不過必須轉營"},{"pid":"b683653480fb3e978602e849c840e9c82026598c","tid":1742821,"uid":340458,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c47a7d8030cdb6c68bef3cea24caecf207a95e7","tid":1742821,"uid":326017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"黎明行動可以唔停<br />\n同意過份針對罷工罷課<br />\n呢2樣影響民生<br />\n冇人針對罷市<br />\n中共真春袋 黎緊仲要阿里巴巴上市"},{"pid":"217245816a54bf7819ef31003c1ca5fac50b8cc4","tid":1742821,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"1. 反對繼續<br />\n<br />\n[後續] 呼籲立即煞停黎明行動 立即作出檢討 擾民而且對政權無效果 樹敵更多 制止學生被撚係被狗咬 同時召喚連仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742706</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n樓主提既目標完全係推人去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極強24小時保安+朝早條街無人係死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f16b802f164193462aebcbe99836baf9ac086d5","tid":1742821,"uid":63822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b683653480fb3e978602e849c840e9c82026598c","tid":1742821,"uid":340458,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得應該集中搞個市<br />\n<br />\n第一個市對中共經濟打擊係最大<br />\n<br />\n第二搞個市對平民既影響相對細好多好多好多"},{"pid":"b316ddf3187a794d9034f89ee4505c0a1d397b7a","tid":1742821,"uid":340458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"211274ec73b45ec7ef4914176a749ff6bec11f3b","tid":1742821,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"217245816a54bf7819ef31003c1ca5fac50b8cc4","tid":1742821,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"1. 反對繼續<br />\n<br />\n[後續] 呼籲立即煞停黎明行動 立即作出檢討 擾民而且對政權無效果 樹敵更多 制止學生被撚係被狗咬 同時召喚連仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742706</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n樓主提既目標完全係推人去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極強24小時保安+朝早條街無人係死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"第一點，我都有同該post樓主討論，可以自己睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n第二點，同71入立會時反對一方論點一樣<br />\n<br />\n切記我只係提出意見，手足亦唔係冇腦唔識思考，做唔做係手足自己決定<br />\n<br />\n再者高風險既野就唔做咁我地好難有突破<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我亦有講過自己腦力有限希望集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n我唔介意大家ban我idea，不過希望ban完之後提出更好既方案"},{"pid":"bef6aac37ef3a2423c41d7709dc93d9d13c00597","tid":1742821,"uid":148355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"塞還塞，日日都號稱三罷根本攬炒埋黃絲經濟圈。藍絲港豬照開工，得黃店陪你罷，呢點絕對應該檢討"},{"pid":"3bc97655c3385db637c242fee4465b69f88d049a","tid":1742821,"uid":94069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"推，有用過d叫停撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0fd0cee6f69bbdfc809e5dd3e63423c7b4fdc3","tid":1742821,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bc97655c3385db637c242fee4465b69f88d049a","tid":1742821,"uid":94069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"推，有用過d叫停撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"我最睇唔起ban人idea但又提唔出更好建議既人"},{"pid":"9fb346a34434ed3833829e372b7d77f61800677b","tid":1742821,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5bd0ae7229ac5f71fb457a64d33851b8e4f9518","tid":1742821,"uid":248834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14f187a3477f80f3546e235ed1dbc48a8107b15","tid":1742821,"uid":149034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}